{"thag7.3:0.1":"Theragatha 7.3 ","thag7.3:0.2":"Sattakanipata ","thag7.3:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag7.3:0.4":"Bhaddattheragatha ","thag7.3:1.1":"“Ekaputto aham asim, ","thag7.3:1.2":"piyo matu piyo pitu; ","thag7.3:1.3":"Bahuhi vatacariyahi, ","thag7.3:1.4":"laddho ayacanahi ca. ","thag7.3:2.1":"Te ca mam anukampaya, ","thag7.3:2.2":"atthakama hitesino; ","thag7.3:2.3":"Ubho pita ca mata ca, ","thag7.3:2.4":"buddhassa upanamayum. ","thag7.3:3.1":"‘Kiccha laddho ayam putto, ","thag7.3:3.2":"sukhumalo sukhedhito; ","thag7.3:3.3":"Imam dadama te natha, ","thag7.3:3.4":"jinassa paricarakam’. ","thag7.3:4.1":"Sattha ca mam patiggayha, ","thag7.3:4.2":"anandam etadabravi; ","thag7.3:4.3":"‘Pabbajehi imam khippam, ","thag7.3:4.4":"hessatyajaniyo ayam’. ","thag7.3:5.1":"Pabbajetvana mam sattha, ","thag7.3:5.2":"viharam pavisi jino; ","thag7.3:5.3":"Anoggatasmim suriyasmim, ","thag7.3:5.4":"tato cittam vimucci me. ","thag7.3:6.1":"Tato sattha nirakatva, ","thag7.3:6.2":"patisallanavutthito; ","thag7.3:6.3":"‘Ehi bhadda’ti mam aha, ","thag7.3:6.4":"sa me asupasampada. ","thag7.3:7.1":"Jatiya sattavassena, ","thag7.3:7.2":"laddha me upasampada; ","thag7.3:7.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","thag7.3:7.4":"aho dhammasudhammata”ti. ","thag7.3:7.5":"… Bhaddo thero …. "}